mercy of a hulking psychopathic killer when they're 
ordered to clean the abandoned Blackwell Hotel as 
an act of community service. The madman (played by 
World Wrestling Entertainment superstar Kane) has 
a steel plate in his head and murder on his mind, 
but can the veteran police officer (Matthew Okine) 
who put a bullet in his brain years before help the 
scrappy teens save one of their own?
